##  Module Purpose

Leadership in risk management begins with **awareness** â€” knowing not just how to document risk, but **when** to raise the flag.

This module teaches you how to recognize the **exact moments** when a POA&M must be opened. Miss the trigger, and you miss the chance to control risk.

> âœ… *Strong GRC leaders donâ€™t wait for audits to act â€” they anticipate, document, and lead from the front.*

